            range depends on the assay(s) used and the quality of the flanking
            sequence. Sequence identified as 'inferred from reference' is
            consistent with GRCh38, and included due to the generated sequence
            either not meeting the required 50bp length for GenBank records or
            the ISFG minimum range.##Bracketing of the minimum and full
            reported sequences is performed by STRNaming PMID:35994887, which
            is consistent with the guidance of the ISFG (International Society
