            results differ between the minimum and full ranges. The reported
            bracketing does not necessarily match the length-based allele
            size.##The ISFG min. range codes are calculated using the sequence
            identifier (SID) algorithm described in PMID:31207427, with only
            the first 5 characters of the SID reported here.##This information
